definition: to send out/to show (one's feeling)/to issue/to develop/to make a bundle of money/classifier for gunshots (rounds)

sentences.english: I feel uneasy whenever I meet the manager.
sentences.chinese: 我一見到這種難做的題目，心裏就開始發怵。

sentences.english: Meeting new people is fun. But it can also induce nervousness.
sentences.chinese: 與人交往是很有趣的，不過難免也會緊張發怵。
